334
00:40:44,680 --> 00:40:46,200
"Bulan baru membentuk semula dunia."

335
00:40:46,720 --> 00:40:50,160
Sejak Batu Oracle
memberikan nubuatan sedemikian,

336
00:40:50,960 --> 00:40:52,360
